&lt;h1 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role is on site in Pleasanton, California&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
