&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;AI is changing the world — and at&amp;nbsp;Tekion,&amp;nbsp;we’re&amp;nbsp;shaping how our people grow with it.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is not a role about replacing what Tekionites do. It’s about expanding what they’re capable of.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
