&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This a brand-new role on a newly formed team — which means you’ll be building from the ground up, with the full support of the CPO and senior leadership. Some things are still taking shape, and that’s intentional: we want someone who thrives in that kind of environment, brings structure where it’s needed, and stays energized by ambiguity rather than derailed by it.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
