&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Workforce Planning &amp;amp; Job Architecture&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Build and&amp;nbsp;maintain&amp;nbsp;a forward-looking workforce planning framework that maps current talent capabilities against future AI-augmented skill needs&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;
