&lt;p&gt;If you would like to be considered for a position at Tekion within the United Kingdom but don&#39;t currently see any roles posted that seem like a fit, please submit your interest by applying to this post. We will add you to our talent network and may reach out if we open up a role that aligns with your experience. Please continue to keep an eye on our careers website as we are always adding new opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
